div.div:
DLUHC DELTA Infrastructure
The infrastructure is defined as code with Terraform
https://github.com/communitiesuk/delta-common-infrastructure
Two AWS accounts are used, one for production and one for non-production (test and staging).These are both under the DLUHC AWS Organization and all users log in through the organisation account.
Each externally accessible application (Delta website, API, Keycloak, CPM) has its own CloudFront distribution, all of them are protected by AWS WAF
CPM, the API and Keycloak are all IP restricted using AWS WAF
The public ALBs only accept requests from our CloudFront distributions, based on a key in a header
